{{单双书号转换|'''安潔莉娜'''}}（{{lang-en|"Angelia"}}）是由美國歌手[[理查·馬克斯|理查·馬克斯]]錄製的[[谣曲|谣曲]]，也是他第二張專輯《[[重犯_(理查·馬克斯專輯)|重犯]]》（''Repeat Offender''）中收錄的第三首歌。[[邁克爾·蘭道|邁克爾·蘭道]]（Michael Landau）在該歌中獨自彈奏了吉他<ref>{{cite web|title=Richard Marx – Repeat Offender|url=https://www.discogs.com/Richard-Marx-Repeat-Offender/release/4093721|access-date=2020-11-11|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222064151/https://www.discogs.com/Richard-Marx-Repeat-Offender/release/4093721|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

〈安潔莉娜〉的製作和聲音也是理查·馬克斯在錄製《重犯》時最為滿意<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KZfZduDPL5E|title = Richard Marx Interview KQCK Radio Stations|date = 2014-07-22|accessdate = 2015-09-24|website = YouTube|publisher = Joe Carreiro (youtube.com)|last = Carreiro|first = Joe|archive-date = 2016-03-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325105005/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KZfZduDPL5E|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

